msgid "URL that display the Mobile version of the map for Android"
msgstr "URL that display the Mobile version of the map for Android"

msgid "CSS class for redirect"
msgstr "CSS class for redirect"

msgid "Add this class to any element to enable the redirect to the URLs above (based on device). You can use it on: a menu item (e.g. in Appearance → Menus, in \"CSS Classes\"), on a link, on a button, or on a container that wraps a link. The link opens in a new tab."
msgstr "Add this class to any element to enable the redirect to the URLs above (based on device). You can use it on: a menu item (e.g. in Appearance → Menus, in \"CSS Classes\"), on a link, on a button, or on a container that wraps a link. The link opens in a new tab."

